---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="SessionFS — Capture, sync, and resume AI coding sessions" description="Background daemon that captures AI coding sessions from 8 tools. Resume anywhere, hand off to teammates, audit for hallucinations. Free and open source.">
<!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">
        Stop re-prompting.<br>Start resuming.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8" style="color: #c9d1d9;">
        SessionFS captures your AI coding sessions and makes them portable, searchable, and verifiable across tools and teammates.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center mb-8">
        <a href="/quickstart/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:brightness-110 transition" style="background: #4f9cf7;">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/SessionFS/sessionfs" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:border-gray-400 transition" style="border: 1px solid #30363d; color: #e6edf3;">
          View on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-sm" style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #c9d1d9;">
        <span>Claude Code</span><span>Codex</span><span>Gemini</span><span>Copilot</span><span>Cursor</span><span>Amp</span><span>Cline</span><span>Roo Code</span>
        <span style="color: #9ca3af;">· 848 tests · Enterprise tested</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- Feature Grid -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-14" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">Everything you need</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#9729;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Cloud Sync</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Push to the cloud, pull on any machine. Auto-sync available.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#128101;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Team Handoff</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Hand off sessions with full context. Session data copies to recipient.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#128269;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Session Search</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Full-text search across all sessions. Find that fix from last week.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#9881;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">MCP Server</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Your AI agent remembers past sessions and project context via MCP.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#9878;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">LLM Judge</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Catch what the AI got wrong. Severity-classified findings with evidence.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#128203;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Session Summary</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">See what happened in 10 seconds. Files, tests, commands extracted automatically.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#128279;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">GitHub &amp; GitLab</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">AI session context on every PR and MR. Contradictions surfaced for reviewers.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><div class="text-2xl mb-3">&#128194;</div><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Workspace Aware</h3><p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Git state captured automatically. Branch, commit, dirty files recorded.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- Enterprise -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">Deploy anywhere. Control everything.</h2>
      <p class="mb-14 max-w-lg mx-auto" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Self-hosted Kubernetes deployment with Helm. Your data stays on your infrastructure.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="glass p-6 text-left"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Self-hosted</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Deploy to any Kubernetes cluster — AWS EKS, GCP GKE, or on-prem. Helm chart, enterprise-tested.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 text-left"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Git integration</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">AI session context on every PR (GitHub) and MR (GitLab). Audit findings surfaced inline.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6 text-left"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Your LLM gateway</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Bring your own LLM — Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section id="pricing" class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">Free during beta.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4 max-w-lg mx-auto" style="color: #c9d1d9;">
        Local capture, cloud sync, team handoff, session search, MCP, LLM Judge, and session summary — all included. No credit card. No limits.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base mb-10" style="color: #9ca3af;">
        Paid plans with storage-based pricing are coming after beta.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href="/quickstart/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:brightness-110 transition" style="background: #4f9cf7;">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@sessionfs.dev?subject=SessionFS%20Pro%20Waitlist" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:border-gray-400 transition" style="border: 1px solid #30363d; color: #e6edf3;">
          Join Waitlist for Pro
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
